name: WAVE
description: WaveWorld is the first platform uniting GameFi, DeFi, and AI Smart Trading Solution on Sui and MOVE ecosystems, allowing users to trade in a smart and easy way while maximizing profits facilitated by the AI trading tools. Accessible via Telegram, Twitter, LINE, WaveWorld enables both Web2 and Web3 users to easily and conveniently access the blockchain ecosystem without the need for additional applications.
